ve - the voiD editor
====================

1. INSTALL

 + ve requires PHP5 and ARC2 (http://arc.semsol.org/download)
 + copy the content of this dir (index.html and interface.js) into any directory of your Webserver
 + copy the content of the server/ dir in a PHP enabled directory of your Webserver
 + adapt the first line of service.php (include_once("C:/Program Files/Apache Software Foundation/Apache2.2/htdocs/arc2/ARC2.php");) to point to your ARC2 directory
 + replace all occurrences of 'http://143.224.254.32/ve/service.php?' in wrapper.php to point to your URI
 + enjoy!